var series = [];

data.vessels.forEach(function (vessel, i) {
    var seriesData = vessel.trips.reduce(function (acc, cur) {
        var startTime = cur.start;
        var points = [];
        cur.voyages.forEach(function (voyage) {
            if (voyage.loadDuration) {
                voyage.loadDuration *= 1000 * 60 * 60;
                points.push({
                    x: startTime,
                    x2: startTime + voyage.loadDuration,
                    y: i
                });
                startTime += voyage.loadDuration;
            }
            voyage.duration *= 1000 * 60 * 60;
            points.push({
                x: startTime,
                x2: startTime + voyage.duration,
                y: i
            });
            startTime += voyage.duration;

            if (voyage.unloadDuration) {
                voyage.unloadDuration *= 1000 * 60 * 60;
                points.push({
                    x: startTime,
                    x2: startTime + voyage.unloadDuration,
                    y: i
                });
                startTime += voyage.unloadDuration + 1000 * 60 * 60 * 48;
            }
        });
        return acc.concat(points);
    }, []);
    series.push({
        name: vessel.name,
        data: seriesData
    });
});
